fix: resolve 500 errors and improve error resilience

- Fix invalid FRED series ID (MANBUSIMSA → TCU) causing 400 Bad Request
- Fix delisted Japan TOPIX ticker (2800.T → 1306.T)
- Add graceful degradation for OpenAI API failures (quota, auth, rate limit)
  across all analyzers (country, sector, stock, forecast, sentiment)
- Return partial data (market data, charts, Fear & Greed) when LLM unavailable
- Replace text-based calendar with visual calendar grid (month view with
  event dots, date selection, sidebar event details)
- Add warning color system (CSS + Tailwind) for LLM unavailability banner
- Improve frontend error handling with retry button and descriptive messages
